# Draft:President Channel

President Channel (also known by its YouTube username @ilovetech237) was a nonprofit YouTube channel that operated from September 1, 2022, to April 16, 2024. The channel was primarily focused on creating and sharing deepfake content and historical presentations using Wombo AI technology. During its active period, the channel produced over 200 videos.
Content and focus
The channel specialized in creating content that utilized artificial intelligence and deepfake technology to produce historical presentations and other related media. Its content revolved around the application of Wombo AI, an AI-powered tool known for creating animated images from static photos.
History
President Channel began operations on September 1, 2022, and remained active until April 16, 2024. Throughout its approximately 19-month existence, the channel maintained a consistent output of AI-generated content, ultimately creating more than 200 videos before ceasing operations.
